Sources and third-party rights
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The SBBD full-text corpus (release/data/corpus_sbbd.jsonl) is derived from
papers published in the SBC Open Library (https://sol.sbc.org.br), which are
openly accessible. Bibliometric metadata is derived from OpenAlex
(https://openalex.org) and Semantic Scholar (https://www.semanticscholar.org).

The VLDB full text is NOT redistributed in this repository because the
Proceedings of the VLDB Endowment are subject to their own copyright terms.
Only aggregated/derived outputs (topic assignments, labels, and OpenAlex
metadata) are included. The VLDB full-text corpus can be reconstructed locally
from vldb.org using the scripts provided (download_vldb.py, extract_text_vldb.py).
